data.description: 6.93 Acres in Daleville School dist w/pond, woods, creek, clubhouse, pole barn, above ground pool, fruit trees & more! This 5 BD, 3 Full BA offers 2280 sf on main & upper level & 1440sf walk-out Basement! Large center island in KT w/stainless appliances, tile floor & Breakfast nook opens to massive versatile Greatroom w/ pass-thru, storage galore, spectacular views & gorgeous brushed laminate! Upstairs 2 huge BD's also w/ beautiful views & walk-in closets. Walk-out Basement w/corner Living Rm fireplace & tile floor. Master w/ walk-in shower, tile surround  & walk-in closet. 2 more spacious BD's! Laundry Rm on main level!Multi level decks surround above ground pool! Pole barn w/electricity. Over an acre of woods! lovely path to pond & creek!
